recepiesData.title: Whole-Grain Banana Bread
recepiesData.description: This one-bow! banana bread — our 2018 Recipe of the Year — uses the simplest ingredients, but is incredibly moist and flavorful.While the recipe calls for a 50/50 mix of flours (all-purpose and whole wheat), we often make the bread 100% whole wheat, and honestly? No one can tell, it's that good! And not only is this bread delicious — it's versatile.
